plus: function(a, b) { var arg = []; arg[0] = 1*arguments[0] + 1*arguments[1]; arg[1]=arguments.length; arg[2]='+'; return arg; }
minus: function(a, b) { var arg = []; arg[0] = 1*arguments[0] - 1*arguments[1]; arg[1]=arguments.length; arg[2]='-'; return arg; }
multiplication: function(a, b) { var arg = []; arg[0] = 1*arguments[0] + 1*arguments[1]; arg[1]=arguments.length; arg[2]='*'; return arg; }
division: function(a, b) { var arg = []; arg[0] = NaN; if (arguments[1]!=0) arg[0] = arguments[0]/arguments[1]; arg[1]=arguments.length; arg[2]='//'; return arg }
